edu.ncsu.csc216.bbtp

Class BBTP

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • edu.ncsu.csc216.bbtp.BBTP
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.util.Observer

    public class BBTP
extends java.util.Observable
implements java.io.Serializable, java.util.Observer
    The main class for the BBTP tools. Holds references to the top-level data structures that contain TestCase and TestingType objects and acts as the controller between the model and the GUI presentation view.
